&lt;p&gt;Make sure to set the prefix to whatever your project prefix is. You can find your project prefix by searching for “prefix” in your angular.json file. It should be whatever you passed to the &lt;code&gt;--prefix&lt;/code&gt; flag when you created the angular project with &lt;code&gt;ng new&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At this point I would commit my progress in preparation for the next step. Again, using the alias commands from my .bashrc file.&lt;/p&gt;
